room_title: Escape room "The Cabin" by Auburn Escape Zones in Auburn
room_description: You were returning from a trip to your uncle's hunting camp when one of your friends got bitten by a venomous snake, a Timber rattlesnake. There is no cell phone coverage, and each minute counts with your friend's life on the line! You remember that your uncle kept an anti-venom somewhere in his cabin. You have 60 minutes to find it and save your friend.
